* [[Reactive hypoglycemia|Reactive (or post-prandial) hypoglycemia]]<ref name="pmid5086042">{{cite journal |author=Hofeldt FD, Dippe S, Forsham PH |title=Diagnosis and classification of reactive hypoglycemia based on hormonal changes in response to oral and intravenous glucose administration |journal=Am. J. Clin. Nutr. |volume=25 |issue=11 |pages=1193–201 |year=1972 |pmid=5086042 |url=http://www.ajcn.org/cgi/reprint/25/11/1193.pdf |format=PDF}}</ref>
